nbsOdsysCcEntry.name: nbsOdsysCcEntry
nbsOdsysCcEntry.description: Status information for a particular control card slot/bay. When a control card is present, it will also have entries in nbsPartHardTable, nbsPartFirmTable, and nbsPartProgTable. The events nbsOdsysTrapCcFailed, nbsOdsysTrapCcRestored, nbsOdsysTrapCcRemoved and nbsOdsysTrapCcInserted indicate changes in nbsOdsysCcOperationalStatus.
